54/* glcorearb.h is for use with OpenGL core profile implementations.
55** It should should be placed in the same directory as gl.h and
56** included as <GL/glcorearb.h>.
57**
58** glcorearb.h includes only APIs in the latest OpenGL core profile
59** implementation together with APIs in newer ARB extensions which
60** can be supported by the core profile. It does not, and never will
61** include functionality removed from the core profile, such as
62** fixed-function vertex and fragment processing.
63**
64** Do not #include both <GL/glcorearb.h> and either of <GL/gl.h> or
65** <GL/glext.h> in the same source file.
66*/
67

75 * Extensions removed: _nomatch_^
76 */
